data.description: Calling All Investors! This is a great opportunity to make a quick return on your investment! This property is a One Story, 3 bedroom, 1 bath Rambler (with Cellar) in Hollywood. There is a detached 1 car garage. The lot is .63 of an acre, and there is no HOA. This property needs a Complete renovation/rehab. Please be advised, there is significant water intrusion, existing mold, and the house is uninhabitable. Excellent Location!  UPDATE: There are multiple offers on this property. Please have all offers submitted by Sunday 12/17 at 12:00 NOON.
